node.text: @lafashionpr ~~ #Oscar nominated Actress #MinnieDriver, #ChiaraFerragni, #OliviaWilde, #RachelBilson and #JanuaryJones were among the MaxMara clad attendees who turned out to the #ChateauMarmont in #WestHollywood to celebrate the #Italian label’s #WomenInFilm.  Guests included #StormReid, #CamilaMendes, #MadelainePetsch, #RebeccaGayheart, #AliceEve, #OliviaHolt, #SukiWaterhouse, #ZoeListerJones and #MeToo movement founder Tarana Burke. Others decked out in looks by the brand were Women in Film L.A. board president Amy Baer as well as #AlexandraDaddario, #LucyHale, #CamilaMorrone, #XoshaRoquemore, #SkaiJackson, #SydneySweeney and #FuschiaKateSumner. #WIF #instylemagazine gettyfashion #genechangfashionpr
